0are%20all%20very%20accessible%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20stardom%20is%20very%20reduced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20were%20made%20at%20a%20time%20-%202014%20-%20when%20neither%20the%20film%20industry%20had%20a%20phenomenon%20called%20OTT%2C%20nor%20the%20world%20had%20survived%20a%20pandemic%20called%20Covid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20Arjun%20Kapoor%20was%20judged%20for%20those%20comments%20on%20social%20media%20(trolling%20was%20not%20as%20alien%20as%20OTT%20back%20then).%20He%20lacked%20the%20%26quot%3Bwillingness%26quot%3B%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20match%20up%20to%20the%20stardom%20of%20the%20Khans%20-%20was%20the%20Internet's%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20did%20the%20Internet%20realise%20that%20Arjun%20Kapoor%20had%20actually%20spoken%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStardom%20doesn't%20go%20away.%20But%20it's%20now%20fragmented%2C%20reduced%20and%20its%20dimensions%20have%20changed%20drastically%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20it%20not%20been%20the%20case%2C%20why%20did%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20daughter%20Suhana%20Khan%2C%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20son%20Ibrahim%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20Aamir%20Khan's%20son%20Junaid's%20first%20films%20not%20find%20a%20place%20in%20theatres%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20their%20films%20don't%20speak%20for%20themselves%2C%20their%20Instagram%20profiles%20will%2C%20as%20will%20their%20strong%20PR%20machineries.%20Film%20business%20is%2C%20after%20all%2C%20no%20longer%20about%20only%20acting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202000%2C%20star%20kids%20like%20Hrithik%20Roshan%2C%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20and%20Abhishek%20Bachchan%20made%20their%20debuts%20on%20the%20big%20screen.%20Nobody%20achieved%20the%20kind%20of%20success%20that%20Hrithik%20Roshan%20did%20with%20his%20maiden%20film%2C%20%3Cem%3EKaho%20Naa%20Pyaar%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Nonetheless%2C%20star%20kids%20were%20being%20launched%20in%20theatres.%20Back%20then%2C%20neither%20did%20OTT%20exist%2C%20nor%20did%20actors%20have