%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20feasibility%20and%20urgency%20of%20an%20OTT%20launch%2C%20film%20critic%20Saibal%20Chatterjee%20tells%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%26quot%3BOTT%20eco-system%20is%20safer%20and%20it%20has%20a%20longer%20run.%20They%20are%20not%20immediately%20being%20judged%20on%20how%20much%20money%20their%20films%20are%20minting%20at%20the%20box%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSocial%20media%20will%20comment%20about%20their%20work.%20But%20they%20are%20there%20for%20a%20longer%20period.%20It's%20a%20far%20more%20convenient%20way%20to%20launch%20a%20career%20and%20it%20will%20remain%20so%20in%20a%20foreseeable%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Chatterjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20trade%20analyst%20Komal%20Nahta%20speaks%20about%20the%20role%20of%20market%20and%20commerce%20which%20drives%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20accepted%20formula%20now.%20OTT%20pays%20big%20money.%20The%20amount%20is%20so%20huge%20that%20producers%20succumb%20to%20the%20temptation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nahta%20tells%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCinema%20is%20cinema.%C2%A0We%20all%20are%20accustomed%20with%20theatrical%20releases.%20But%20if%20a%20film%20is%20not%20commercially%20viable%20to%20release%20in%20theatres%2C%20the%20debutant%20has%20to%20be%20content%20with%20the%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Nahta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20the%20longevity%20factor%2C%20Komal%20Nahta%20tells%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20liked%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Archies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EBut%20nobody's%20career%20is%20finished.%20Suhana%20Khan%20is%20doing%20another%20film.%20One%20of%20Khushi%20Kapoor's%20films%20has%20already%20released%20in%20theatres%20%5B%3Cem%3ELoveyapa%3C%2Fem%3E%5D.%20Another%20film%20releases%20today%20%5B%3Cem%3ENadaaniyan%3C%2Fem%3E%5D.%20So%2C%20the%20fear%20of%20being%20dismissed%20with%20one%20film%20is%20not%20there.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20Stardom%20Compromised%20For%20Star%20Kids%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20question%20with%20which%20we%20began%20this%20piece%2C%20is%20the%20fate%20of%20stardom%20in%20the%20era%20of%20reels%20and%C2%A0%20omnipresent%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilm%20critic%20Saibal%20Chatterjee%20tells%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20Manoj%20Bajpayee%20is%20a%20star.%20Jaideep%20Ahlawat%20is%20a%20star%20on%20OTT.%20But%20their%20stardom%20is%20not%20that%20of%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20or%20Rajesh%20Khanna.%20So%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20stardom%20is%20now%20fragmented.%20It%20doesn't%20go%20away%20but%20the%20shape%20and%20size%20of%C2%A0%20stardom%20have%20undergone%20a%20drastic%20change%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20debutant%20I%20can%20think%20of%2C%20who%20churned%20a%20blockbuster%20with%20his%20maiden%20release%2C%20is%20Hrithik%20Roshan.%20That%20too%2C%2025%20years%20ago.%20We%20didn't%20have%20a%20star%20of%20that%20stature%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20Talk%20about%20Rajkummar%20Rao%20or%C2%A0Ayushmann%20Khurrana%20-%20they%20have%20their%20own%20journey.%20None%20of%20them%20was%20a%20star%20with%20their%20first%20films%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Saibal%20Chatterjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETracing%20the%20evolution%20of%20stardom%20over%20the%20years%2C%20Saibal%20Chatterjee%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BStardom%20is%20redefined%20by%20technology.%20When%20multiplexes%20came%20into%20the%20picture%2C%20we%20thought%20there%20would%20be%20space%20for%20all%20kinds%20of%20films.%20But%20eventually%20big%20banner%20films%20swept%20the%20smaller%20ones.%20Now%2C%20stardom%20is%20defined%20by%20easier%20availability%20of%20stars.%20They%20are%20on%20your%20phones%2C%20they%20are%20coming%20to%20your%20living%20rooms.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20times%2C%20stars%20are%20also%20talking%20to%20you%20directly%20on%20phones%2C%20courtesy%2C%20Instagram%20Lives%20or%20Ask%20Me%20Anything%20sessions%20on%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Room%20For%20Hindi%20Films%20In%20Theatres%2C%20South%20Rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECall%20it%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPushpa%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20wave%20or%20a%20renewed%20interest%20in%20Southern%20potboilers%2C%20there's%20a%20paradigm%20shift%20in%20the%20way%20Hindi%20films%20are%20being%20made%2C%20consumed%20and%20sold%20across%20various%20platforms.%20While%20the%20South%20is%20still%20churning%20films%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Epaisa-vasool%3C%2Fem%3E%20theatrical%20experience%2C%20typical%20commercial%20Hindi%20films%20are%20not%20being%20released%20in%20theatres%20without%20a%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20big-budget%2C%20big%20star-driven%20Hindi%20films%20bombed%20at%20the%20box%20office%20in%20recent%20past.%20Last%20year's%20Diwali%20release%2C%20%3Cem%3ESingham%20Again%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20the%20biggest%20example%20of%20this%20genre.%20A%20successful%20franchise%2C%20a%20star%20cast%20boasting%20of%20Ranveer%20Singh%2C%20Deepika%20Padukone%2C%20Ajay%20Devgn%2C%20Akshay%20Kumar%2C%20Tiger%20Shroff%20in%20the%20lead%20-%20no%20factor%20worked%20in%20the%20film's%20favour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20dominance%20of%20South%20at%20the%20theatres%2C%20Saibal%20Chatterjee%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BTake%2C%20for%20example%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPushpa%202%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20was%20meant%20for%20the%20big%20screen%20and%20it%20smashed%20all%20records.%20It%20has%20come%20to%20an%20OTT%20platform%20but%20it's%20not%20made%20for%20OTT.%20Now%2C%20Ibrahim%20Ali%20Khan%20can't%20fight%20against%20a%20%3Cem%3EPushpa%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3EChhaava%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20theatres%20with%20his%20debut%20film.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20OTT%20is%20a%20saving%20grace%20-%20for%20star%20kids%2C%20for%20producers%20and%20for%20everyone%20in%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20OTT%20Launch%20A%20Boon%20Or%20Bane%20For%20Star%20Kids%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20safe%20launch%20is%20fun.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20ensure%20the%20high%20which%20comes%20with%20overnight%20fame%20and%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKomal%20Nahta%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20boon%20for%20star%20kids.%20But%20it%20has%20its%20flip%20side%20too.%20There's%20no%20box%20office%20pressure.%20So%2C%20the%20excitement%20is%20also%20reduced.%20The%20box%20office%20pumps%20up%20the%20excitement%20to%20a%20certain%20extent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202023%2C%20the%C2%A0premiere%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Archies%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20a%20mega%20event%20where%20the%20Bachchans%20flashed%20their%20best%20smiles%20for%20the%20camera%2C%20hiding%20the%20rumoured%20rifts%20in%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%C2%A0Nikhil%20Nanda%2C%20who%20is%20hardly%20seen%20at%20the%20Bachchan%20gatherings%2C%20to%20Aishwarya%20Rai%20Bachchan%20-%20everyone%20showed%20up%20for%20Agastya%20Nanda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Bachchans%20at%20The%20Archies%20premiere%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Bachchans%20at%20The%20Archies%20premiere%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fkmfcje4o_ar_625x300_07_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bachchans%20at%20The%20Archies%20premiere%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Loveyapa%3C%2Fem%3E's%20theatrical%20release%2C%20Aamir%20Khan%20hosted%20several%20screenings%20to%20boost%20his%20son's%20confidence.%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Salman%20Khan%20too%20were%20on%20the%20guest%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20stars%20can%20push%20for%20a%20theatrical%20release%20for%20their%20children's%20films%2C%C2%A0Komal%20Nahta%20tells%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENDTV%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%26quot%3BThey'll%20do%20everything%20to%20pep%20up%20and%20boost%20their%20child.%20They'll%20go%20all%20the%20way%20to%2