0defend%20our%20sovereignty%2C%20we%20will%20defend%20our%20jobs.%20We%20will%20defend%20our%20way%20of%20living.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20begun%20boycotting%20American%20products.%20Liquor%20vends%20in%20Ontario%20removed%20Kentucky%20whiskies%20and%20Californian%20wines%20after%20state%20premier%20Doug%20Ford%20ordered%20them%20out.%20Ford%20also%20imposed%20a%2025%25%20tariff%20on%20electricity%20exports%20to%20the%20US.%20A%20pizza%20chain%20has%20dropped%20Costco%20as%20a%20supplier.%20Alberta%20premier%20Danielle%20Smith%20also%20announced%20hard-hitting%20tariffs%20on%20US%20products%20and%20an%20outright%20ban%20on%20American%20liquor.%20Several%20retail%20outlets%20now%20sport%20Buy%20Canadian%20tags.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20Backs%20Off%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELo%20and%20behold%2C%20Trump%20hit%20pause%2C%20suspending%20the%20tariffs%20by%20a%20month%20and%20giving%20bilateral%20discussions%20a%20chance.%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%20told%20%3Cem%3EFox%20TV%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20administration%20is%20trying%20to%20hammer%20out%20a%20deal%20with%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwork%20something%20out%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20trade%20tariff%20strategy%20is%20said%20to%20be%20a%20multi-purpose%20instrument.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20such%20as%20India%2C%20it%20is%20intended%20to%20open%20up%20the%20market%20for%20American%20companies.%20In%20others%2C%20such%20as%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%2C%20it%20is%20about%20shutting%20out%20competition%20as%20well%20as%20unproven%20pet%20peeves%2C%20such%20as%20loose%20regulation%20of%20cross-border%20drug%20trafficking.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20China%2C%20tariffs%20are%20meant%20to%20both%20strangle%20competition%20as%20well%20as%20ensure%20national%20security%20objectives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDOGE%20Troubles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President's%20other%20major%20initiative%2C%20the%20Elon%20Musk-led%20DOGE%20or%20Department%20Of%20Government%20Efficiency%2C%20has%20a%20much%20bigger%20and%20longer-term%20objective%2C%20reengineering%20multiple%20institutions%20to%20fit%20into%20a%20libertarian%20framework.%20That%20too%20is%20not%20going%20well.%20After%20Musk%20and%20his%20marauding%20troops%20went%20in%20with%20a%20battering%20ram%20and%20broke%20things%2C%20resistance%20is%20coming%20up%2C%20some%20of%20it%20from%20within.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20directions%20from%20Kash%20Patel%20after%20taking%20charge%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20was%20to%20tell%20staff%20to%20ignore%20orders%20from%20DOGE.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20an%20early%20legal%20attempt%20by%2014%20states%20to%20block%20DOGE%E2%80%94whose%20role%20is%20technically%20restricted%20to%20advisory%E2%80%94from%20accessing%20information%20systems%20failed%20in%20a%20federal%20court%2C%20several%20other%20challenges%20that%20rely%20on%20a%20privacy%20law%20are%20pending.%20A%20federal%20judge%20also%20temporarily%20stopped%20DOGE's%20access%20to%20government%20payment%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20appears%20to%20be%20unhappy%20about%20the%20heat%20DOGE%20is%20getting%20even%20as%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20show%20except%20chaos.%20He%20held%20a%20review%20meeting%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20promised%20to%20hold%20it%20every%20two%20weeks%20until%20they%20get%20the%20winnowing%20right.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20secretaries%20learn%20about%2C%20and%20understand%2C%20the%20people%20working%20for%20the%20various%20departments%2C%20they%20can%20be%20very%20precise%20as%20to%20who%20will%20remain%2C%20and%20who%20will%20go.%20We%20say%20the%20%E2%80%98scalpel'%20rather%20than%20the%20%E2%80%98hatchet'%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F114117008305421663%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3Cem%3E%20Financial%20Times%20%3C%2Fem%3Equoted%20him%20telling%20reporters%20that%20he%20did%20not%20want%20good%20people%20to%20go%20in%20big%20indiscriminate%20cuts.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20the%20cabinet%20members%20to%20go%20first%2C%20keep%20all%20the%20people%20you%20want%2C%20everybody%20that%20you%20need.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20Hint%20Of%20Tensions%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20occasion%20where%20a%20crack%20seems%20to%20have%20emerged%20between%20Trump%20and%20Musk%2C%20even%20though%20there%20have%20been%20embarrassing%20moments%20earlier.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20when%20Musk's%20four-year-old%20son%2C%20X%2C%20tramped%20around%20the%20Oval%20Office%20in%20full%20media%20glare%20as%20his%20father%20and%20the%20President%20answered%20journalists'%20queries.%20In%20a%20joint%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fem%3E'%20Sean%20Hannity%2C%20Trump%20and%20Musk%20said%20they%20were%20aware%20of%20gossip%20about%20the%20latter's%20power%20and%20jibes%20that%20the%20President%20was%20a%20mere%20figurehead.%20They%20dismissed%20them%20as%20amateur%20attempts%20to%20drive%20a%20wedge%20between%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWednesday's%20review%20of%20DOGE%20activities%2C%20however%2C%20suggests%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Trump's%20blind%20faith%20in%20Musk%20might%20be%20shaken%20and%20that%20he%20is%20planning%20to%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20personal%20oversight.%20Perhaps%20Musk%20rubbed%20too%20many%20people%20in%20the%20Trump%20team%20on%20the%20wrong%20side.%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20likely%20read%20the%20writing%20on%20the%20wall%20when%20he%20made%20an%20early%20honourable%20exit.%20The%20first%20person%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fce90066b4e20483da79adf21910da0c7%5C%22%3Eto%20exit%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20his%20team%20prematurely%20in%20Trump's%20first%20term%20as%20President%20was%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Michael%20Flynn%2C%20for%20his%20contacts%20with%20Russia.%20Flynn%20was%20of%20a%20similar%20disposition%20as%20Musk%3A%20aggressive%20and%20imperious.%20The%20next%20to%20be%20fired%20was%20FBI%20Director%20James%20Comey%2C%20followed%20by%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Rex%20Tillerson%2C%20and%20then%20Secretary%20of%20Defense%20James%20Mattis.%20All%20of%20them%20were%2C%20in%20one%20way%20or%20another%2C%20let%20go%20of%20over%20issues%20related%20to%20Russia.%20Comey%20was%20fired%20for%20his%20(mis)handling%20of%20the%20investigation%20into%20Hillary%20Clinton's%20emails.%20Although%20differences%20were%20building%20up%2C%20Tillerson's%20departure%20came%20immediately%20after%20he%20spoke%20against%20Russian%20spies%20reportedly%20poisoning%20a%20defector%20and%20his%20daughter%20in%20Salisbury%2C%20England.%20Mattis%20left%20after%20disagreeing%20with%20Trump%20on%20withdrawing%20American%20troops%20from%20Syria%2C%20where%20Russia%20was%20gaining%20the%20upper%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPetulant%20Leaders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20whirlwind%20seven%20weeks%2C%20during%20which%20Trump%20has%20managed%20to%20wreck%20relationships%20and%20destabilise%20long-standing%20institutions%2C%20the%20stock-taking%20might%20have%20begun.%20This%20is%20when%20leaders%20like%20Trump%20become%20impatient%3A%20when%20they%20do%20not%20see%20the%20expected%20results.%20The%20next%20reaction%20would%20likely%20be%20petulance.%20A%20petulant%20bully%20looks%20for%20targets%20to%20pick%20on.%20That's%20what%20Ukraine%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20faced.%20Tiny%20Panama%20could%20be%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20may%20even%20pick%20on%20India%2C%20which%20has%20tried%20to%20stay%20on%20Trump's%20right%20side%20even%20though%20it%20did%20not%20help%20much%20with%20tariffs.%20India%20has%20chosen%20to%20rely%20on%20its%20political%20leaders'%20and%20diplomats'%20persuasive%20powers%20behind%20closed%20doors%20rather%20than%20publicly%20decrying%20Trump's%20actions.%20Foreign%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20has%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20allayed%20Trump's%20fears%20of%20India%2C%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BRICS%20grouping%2C%20in%20any%20way%20trying%20to%20undermine%20the%20US%20dollar.%20But%20it's%20always%20better%20to%20keep%20your%20fingers%20crossed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dinesh%20Narayanan%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20journalist%20and%20author%20of%20'The%20RSS%20And%20The%20Making%20Of%20The%20Deep%20Nation'.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741349520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fkivhnpj8_elon-musk-donald-trump_625x300_07_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fare-we-seeing-the-first-signs-of-a-musk-trump-rift-7869642%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20whirlwind%20seven%20weeks%2C%20during%20which%20Trump%20has%20managed%20to%20wreck%20relationships%20and%20destabilise%20long-standing%20institutions%2C%20the%20stock-taking%20might%20have%20begun.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fare-we-seeing-the-first-signs-of-a-musk-trump-rift-7869642%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beyond%20Financial%20Aid%3A%20The%20Programme%20Helping%2095%25%20of%20Students%20Step%20into%20Careers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Cybage%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20passionate%20about%20engineering%20since%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20but%20growing%20up%20in%20a%20lower-middle-class%20family%2C%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20sure%20if%20that%20dream%20would%20ever%20come%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%2024-year-old%20Fiza%20Shaikh.%20With%20her%20father%20working%20as%20a%20carpenter%20and%20her%20mother%20a%20housewife%2C%20her%20family%20faced%20constant%20financial%20struggles%2C%20leaving%20little%20room%20f