Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20it%20simply%2C%20if%20an%20H-1B%20Visa%20holder%20fails%20to%20get%20a%20Green%20Card%20before%20their%20child%20turns%2021%2C%20the%20latter%20faces%20deportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20are%20now%20exploring%20other%20options%2C%20including%20immigrating%20to%20countries%20like%20Canada%20or%20the%20UK%2C%20which%20have%20more%20flexible%20policies.%20The%20massive%20backlog%20in%20the%20US%20employment-based%20green%20card%20system%20disproportionately%20affects%20Indian%20immigrants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services%20(USCIS)%20recently%20announced%20the%20registration%20period%20for%20H-1B%20visas%20for%20fiscal%20year%202026.%20The%20process%20opens%20on%20March%207%20and%20runs%20through%20March%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDip%20Patel%2C%20the%20Founder%20and%20President%20of%20%3Cem%3EImprove%20The%20Dream%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0a%20grassroots%20organisation%20that%20supports%20and%20advocates%20for%20young%20immigrants%20who%20have%20grown%20up%20in%20the%20United%20States%20as%20children%20of%20long%20term%20visa%20holders%2C%20but%20face%20aging%20out%20of%20the%20immigration%20system%2C%20speaks%20to%20NDTV%20regarding%20the%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20such%20individuals%20and%20issues%20related%20to%20it.%20Here%20are%20some%20excerpts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReports%20suggest%20some%20dependents%20of%20people%20with%20H-1B%20visas%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20'self-deportation'.%20What%20is%20'self%20deportation'%20and%20is%20there%20a%20need%20to%20be%20wary%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAging%20out%20is%20when%20a%20child%20dependent%20on%20a%20visa%20holder%20turns%2021%20and%20ages%20out%20of%20that%20status.%20Due%20to%20the%20green%20card%20backlogs%2C%20there%20are%20many%20Indians%20who%20are%20on%20H-1B%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20sometimes%20decades.%20Their%20young%20children%20who%20were%20brought%20lawfully%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20have%20grown%20up%20on%20a%20H-1B%20dependent%20visa.%20Even%20though%20they%20have%20a%20green%20card%20petition%20pending%2C%20if%20that%20child%20turns%2021%20before%20the%20parent%20receives%20the%20green%20card%2C%20that%20child%20will%20age%20out%20and%20face%20self%20deportation.%20That%20means%2C%20to%20avoid%20making%20it%20documented%20that%20the%20individual%20has%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20or%20find%20another%20way%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20fact%20that%20%26quot%3Baging%20out%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20around%20for%20a%20while%20now%2C%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20ensure%20people%20who%20have%20spent%20almost%20their%20whole%20lives%20in%20the%20US%20are%20not%20deported%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20individuals%20do%20switch%20over%20to%20an%20international%20student%20visa%20temporarily%2C%20but%20after%20that%20if%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20stay%2C%20they%20have%20to%20leave.%20Unfortunately%20there%20are%20about%2010%2C000%20individuals%20who%20face%20deportation%2C%20even%20though%20they%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20United%20States%20maintaining%20legal%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20basis%20of%20this%20%26quot%3Baging%20out%26quot%3B%20issue%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20inability%20of%20people%20to%20get%20Green%20Cards%3F%20Has%20the%20U.S.%20government%20done%20enough%20to%20tackle%20this%20problem%3F%20Is%20there%20something%20else%20also%20at%20play%20here%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20recent%20change%20on%20self%20deportation%20and%20this%20has%20been%20in%20the%20system%20forever.%20It%20has%20been%20getting%20worse%20since%20the%20last%2010-15%20years%20because%20of%20the%20Green%20Card%20backlog%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20like%20this%20administration%20has%20made%20it%20worse.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20such%20mechanism%20that%20people%20could%20extend%20it%20for%202%20years%20under%20DACA%2C%20that%20only%20applies%20to%20undocumented%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20America's%20Children%20Act%20and%20how%20will%20it%20sort%20this%20problem%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20our%20efforts%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20get%20attention%20to%20this%20and%20get%20bipartisan%20legislation%20in%20Congress%20introduced%20called%20America's%20Children%20Act%2C%20supported%20by%20both%20Republicans%20and%20Democrats.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20bipartisan%20immigration%20bills%20in%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20enable%20children%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20maintained%20lawful%20status%20and%20want%20to%20contribute%20back%20to%20the%20country%2C%20to%20stay%20and%20have%20a%20clear%20pathway%20to%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20America's%20Children%20Act%20will%20make%20sure%20that%20that%20individual%20doesn't%20have%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20and%20their%20green%20card%20application%2C%20which%20had%20been%20pending%2C%20does%20not%20get%20kicked%20out.%20They%20get%20to%20keep%20their%20place%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%20it%20creates%20a%20mechanism%20that%20if%20you%20were%20here%20as%20a%20child%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20attended%20a%20college%2C%20graduated%20university%20and%20been%20here%20for%2010%20years%2C%20then%20you%20can%20apply%20for%20a%20Green%20Card%2C%20and%205%20years%20later%2C%20apply%20for%20citizenship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20important%20is%20immigration%20reform%20for%20the%20United%20States%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20case%20for%20immigration%20reform%20is%20very%20strong.%2010%2C000%20people%20who%20only%20know%20America%20and%20are%20embedded%20in%20American%20culture%20are%20having%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20every%20year.%2090%25%20of%20whom%20are%20either%20in%20STEM%20or%20healthcare%20fields%2C%20how%20does%20that%20help%20the%20United%20States%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20Indians%20in%20the%20U.S.%20need%20to%20be%20worried%20about%20Trump's%20immigration%20crackdown%3F%20He%20has%20said%20that%20he%20will%20welcome%20tech%20graduates%20and%20Ivy%20League%20graduates%20with%20open%20arms%2C%20but%20what%20about%20the%20others%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20word%20-%20immigration%20crackdown%20is%20used%2C%20it%20is%20about%20illegal%20immigration%2C%20not%20legal%20immigration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EReports%20suggest%20a%202-year%20extension%20policy%20is%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20scrapped%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20Can%20you%20shed%20some%20light%20on%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDACA%20was%20a%20program%20for%20undocumented%20children%20that%20were%20brought%20here%2C%20they%20had%20an%20option%20to%20get%20a%202%20year%20work%20permit%20and%20protection%20and%20be%20able%20to%20renew%20it%20every%202%20years.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%20Texas%20court%20case%20that%20is%20against%20DACA%2C%20and%20it%20is%20under%20threat.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741346940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Foceoh97o_us-deportation_625x300_06_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-about-americas-children-act-and-how-it-can-protect-against-deportation-7870011%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Americas%20Children%20Act%20will%20enable%20children%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20maintained%20lawful%20status%20and%20want%20to%20contribute%20back%20to%20the%20country%2C%20to%20stay%20and%20have%20a%20clear%20pathway%20to%20citizenship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-about-americas-children-act-and-how-it-can-protect-against-deportation-7870011%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22