20Bondar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20purchased%20roughly%2010%2C000%20AI-enhanced%20drones%20in%202024.%20Overall%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-world-largest-producer-tactical-strategic-drones-war-russia-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20acquired%20about%202%20million%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20that%20most%20of%20the%20drones%20Ukraine%20is%20using%20to%20fight%20off%20the%20Russians%20are%20still%20entirely%20controlled%20by%20human%20operators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20drones%20are%20largely%20limited%20to%20final-approach%20navigation%2C%20but%20they're%20proving%20their%20worth.%20These%20systems%20demand%20far%20less%20skill%20from%20pilots%2C%20can%20bypass%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhidden-electronic-warfare-battle-demanding-more-of-ukrainian-soldiers-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectronic%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20could%20sever%20the%20drone's%20connection%20to%20the%20operator%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-unjammable-fiber-optic-drone-keep-pace-russia-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20the%20number%20of%20drones%20necessary%20for%20mission%20success%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Bondar%20said%20only%20two%20drones%20could%20do%20what%20might%20otherwise%20take%20eight%20or%20nine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20inspect%20drones%20during%20a%20handover%20from%20a%20volunteer%20organization%20in%20Lviv%20in%20September.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fe307c9e0c5c2eeeea3ea6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoth%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%20have%20been%20intensifying%20their%20deployment%20of%20first-person%20drones%20as%20loitering%20munitions%2C%20with%20companies%20and%20volunteer%20organizations%20on%20both%20sides%20manufacturing%20drone