%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20continued%20flip-flopping%20has%20left%20the%20US%20economy%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20whiplash.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-canada-mexico-business-industry-reaction-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusinesses%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-trade-war-spx-nasdaq-dollar-selloff-correction-nvidia-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarkets%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0have%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20policies%20amid%20a%20budding%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-trade-war-what-it-means-for-consumers-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrade%20war%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economy%20makes%20waves%20across%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tariff%20tension%20between%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretailers-small-businesses-react-trump-trade-tariffs-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENorth%20American%20trade%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20creating%20diplomatic%20friction%20between%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20driving%20cross-industry%20cost%20increases%20and%20consumer%20price%20hikes%2C%20Nick%20Vyas%2C%20the%20founding%20director%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California's%20Randall%20R.%20Kendrick%20Global%20Supply%20Chain%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that's%20a%20feature%20of%20Trump's%20trade%20policy%2C%20not%20a%20bug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20has%20to%20understand%20that%20you're%20on%20the%20long%20ride%20here%20with%20this%20jolt%2C%20this%20is%20not%20just%20turbulence%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%2C%26quot%3B%20Vyas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Trump%20prides%20himself%20on%20being%20a%20master%20dealmaker%2C%20Vyas%20said%20the%20president%20seems%20to%20believe%20he'll%20be%20able%20to%20achieve%20his%20policy%20goals%20by%20increasing%20the%20pressure%20on%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20that%20means%20keeping%20each%20country's%20leader%20off%20balance%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20all%20fits%20into%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-us-stock-market-underperforming-europe-international-trump-america-first-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerica%20First%3C%2Fa%3E%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20Vyas%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20don't%20alienate%20our%20allies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20tariff%20threats%20may%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20strengthen%20the%20US'%20economic%20standing%2C%20Trump's%20repeated%20backtracking%20may%20not%20help%20the%20implementation%20of%20his%20other%20policy%20priorities%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20Andrea%20Schneider%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Kukin%20Program%20for%20Conflict%20Resolution%20at%20the%20Cardozo%20School%20of%20Law%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20threaten%20and%20then%20continue%20to%20walk%20things%20back%2C%20obviously%2C%20the%20threat%20loses%20its%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Schneider%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20strategy%20message%20we're%20trying%20to%20send%20is%20confusing%20and%20is%20less%20strong%20because%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchneider%20said%20the%20mixed%20signals%20and%20confusing%20trade%20policies%20don't%20give%20businesses%20the%20predictability%20needed%20to%20make%20decisions%20like%20hiring%2C%20expanding%20research%20and%20development%2C%20or%20developing%20a%20new%20product.%20These%20factors%20increase%20market%20volatility%2C%20making%20consumers%20unhappy%2C%20and%20can%20drive%20social%20unrest%20as%20prices%20of%20everyday%20goods%20continue%20to%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20is%20watching.%20Markets%20are%20watching%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20chaos%20and%20unpredictability%20might%2C%20in%20certain%20instances%2C%20make%20sense%20in%20diplomatic%20relationships%20or%20one-on-one%20negotiations.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20work%20in%20a%20situation%20like%20this%2C%20where%20every%20US%20business%20is%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do%20tomorrow%20and%20can't%20predict%20what%20the%20policy%20will%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dad215a4-bf21-409f-96d6-114467000167%5C%22%3EA%20game%20of%20tariff%20brinkmanship%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThursday's%20announcement%20is%20the%20second%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-mexico-delayed-month-sheinbaum-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonthlong%20delay%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trump%20has%20imposed%20since%20he%20signed%20executive%20orders%20calling%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-plan-external-revenue-service-imports-impact-consumers-economy-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweeping%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February.%20The%20duties%20%E2%80%94%20including%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Canadian%20and%20Mexican%20goods%20and%2010%25%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20%E2%80%94%20went%20into%20effect%20on%20Tuesday.%20Energy%20products%20from%20Canada%20were%20also%20subjected%20to%20a%20separate%2010%25%20tariff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-retaliate-trump-trade-war-tariffs-soybeans-agriculture-two-sessions-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20and%20Canada%20retaliated%3C%2Fa%3E%20immediately%20on%20Tuesday%20with%20tariffs%20on%20US%20products.%20Mexico%20said%20it%20would%20follow%20suit%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20move%20that%20Gladys%20McCormick%2C%20the%20Moskowitz%20endowed%20chair%20in%20Mexico-US%20relations%20at%20Syracuse%20University%2C%20told%20BI%20was%20likely%20in%20anticipation%20of%20an%20enforcement%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%20with%20you%2C%20I%20wasn't%20surprised%2C%20nor%20do%20I%20think%20Mexicans%20were%20surprised%2C%26quot%3B%20McCormick%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20lag%2C%20in%20essence%2C%20gives%20the%20Trump%20administration%20an%20off-ramp%20to%20really%20kind%20of%20think%20through%20how%20catastrophically%20devastating%20this%20would%20be%20to%20both%20countries%2C%20not%20just%20Mexico.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20playing%20a%20game%20of%20brinkmanship%2C%20or%20pushing%20a%20risky%20situation%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20disaster%20before%20backing%20down%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20a%20positive%20outcome%2C%20which%20has%20been%20an%20%26quot%3Bintrinsic%20part%20of%20the%20Trump%20playbook%2C%26quot%3B%20McCormick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20and%20when%20Trump%20does%20follow%20through%20with%20tariffs%2C%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20this%20sort%20of%20wholesale%2025%25%20on%20everything.%20Rather%2C%20they%20will%20ultimately%20end%20up%20taking%20a%20selective%20approach%20to%20certain%20industries%20or%20certain%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20McCormick%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20I%20think%20that%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20then%20especially%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ceo-trump-tariffs-devastating-auto-industry-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eautomobile%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20be%20so%20severely%20hard%20hit%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border%20that%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20off%20the%20table.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c9e101c-5c10-4b16-9933-99f2ec7f1341%5C%22%3E'This%20is%20very%20much%20about%20political%20theater'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20major%20trading%20partners%20are%20stuck%20in%20a%20battle%20of%20wills%20instigated%20by%20Trump.%20The%20president%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20the%20duties%20will%20help%20drive%20down%20immigration%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-fentanyl-crisis-mexico-canada-harm-reduction-expert-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efentanyl%3C%2Fa%3E%20flowing%20across%20US%20borders.%20However%2C%20Christopher%20Tang%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20scholar%20of%20global%20supply%20chain%20management%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20isn't%20convinced%20that's%20Trump's%20primary%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20claimed%20that%20this%20tariff%20is%20a%20penalty%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-plan-deadline-trade-policies-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanada%20and%20Mexico%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20curb%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20illegal%20drug%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20Tang%20said.%20However%2C%20he%20added%20that%20the%20rates%20of%20crossings%20for%20both%20migrants%20and%20drugs%20are%20down%20at%20both%20borders%2C%20so%20he%20thinks%20that%20rationale%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20excuse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Tang%20said%20he%20believes%20Trump's%20tariffs%20are%20more%20likely%20an%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bclose%20the%20backdoor%26quot%3B%20for%20Chinese%20products%20using%20Mexico%20as%20a%20transition%20point%20to%20avoid%20tariffs.%20China%20has%20used%20Mexico%20as%20a%20workaround%20to%20avoid%20tariffs%20by%20shipping%20the%20parts%20or%20semi-finished%20products%20%E2%80%94%20like%20furniture%20%E2%80%94%20to%20Mexico%2C%20performing%20final%20assembly%20in%20Mexico%2C%20and%20then%20shipping%20the%20finished%20goods%20to%20the%20US%20without%20paying%20its%20own%20tariffs%2C%20Tang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20close%20the%20backdoor%20for%20importing%20Chinese%20goods%20without%20paying%20tariffs%2C%20it%20can%20be%20effective%2C%20but%20the%20implementation%20can%20be%20complicated%20due%20to%20the%20mass%20volume%20and%20limited%20manpower%2C%26quot%3B%20Tang%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20nudge%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20to%20expand%20its%20control%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20and%20illegal%20drugs%2C%20only%20time%20will%20tell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMexico%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20already%20spent%20years%20addressing%20both%20problems%20by%20sending%20its%20National%20Guard%20to%20the%20Mexican-US%20border%20to%20cut%20off%20immigrants%20and%20working%20to%20shutter%20fentanyl%20labs%20in%20the%20nation%2C%20McCormick%2C%20the%20Syracuse%20University%20professor%2C%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20the%20demands%20from%20the%20Trump%20administration%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bvague%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bworrisome%26quot%3B%20to%20those%20who%20wonder%20when%20enough%20will%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20absence%20of%20metrics%20suggests%20that%20this%20is%20not%20about%20fentanyl%20and%20it's%20not%20about%20immigration.%20This%20is%20very%20much%20about%20political%20theater%2C%26quot%3B%20McCormick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-mexico-canada-tariffs-economic-uncertainty-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741342861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ca2800b8b41a9673f9f1b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-mexico-canada-tariffs-economic-uncertainty-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump's%20flip-flopping%20on%20trade%20policy%20has%20left%20the%20market%20struggling%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20his%20latest%20policies%20amid%20a%20budding%20trade%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbalevic%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Balevic%2CKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A142%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-mexico-canada-tariffs-economic-unce