0online%2C%20the%20conversation%20can%20get%20ugly%20when%20it%20concerns%20parents%20who%20share.%20It's%20common%20to%20hear%20that%20parents%20who%20post%20about%20their%20kids%20online%20are%20putting%20their%20children's%20privacy%20and%20personal%20data%20at%20risk%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20parents%20who%20would%20never%20post%20their%20children's%20faces%20or%20any%20identifying%20information%2C%20like%20their%20kid's%20full%20name%2C%20gender%2C%20or%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20or%20disclose%20any%20information%20that%20might%20reveal%20their%20child's%20location%2C%20such%20as%20the%20name%20of%20their%20child's%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20their%20choice%2C%20and%20they're%20free%20to%20make%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e82a3e9c-c8a9-4bb9-bf40-143ee2bde6c8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20me%2C%20the%20rewards%20outweigh%20the%20risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20doctor%20or%20novelist%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20a%20personal%20essayist.%20I've%20made%20a%20career%20from%20telling%20intimate%20stories%20about%20my%20life.%20My%20family's%20stories%20are%20my%20stories%2C%20and%20my%20stories%20pay%20my%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20might%20argue%20that%20I%20could%20hold%20back%20on%20details%2C%20but%20my%20creative%20process%20is%20such%20that%20anything%20could%20become%20content%2C%20and%20details%20make%20a%20narrative%20come%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20respect%20when%20my%20editors%20request%20photos%20to%20illustrate%20my%20stories%20because%20images%20give%20a%20story%20context.%20In%20today's%20media%20landscape%2C%20all%20this%20additional%20labor%20is%20an%20expected%20aspect%20of%20publishing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20afford%20to%20worry%20how%20a%20story%20about%20my%20toddler's%20toilet%20troubles%20might%20dissuade%20a%20recruiter%20from%20offering%20them%20a%20job%20in%2020%20years.%20I%20pitch%20these%20stories%20because%20editors%20buy%20them%2C%20and%20they%20buy%20them%20because%20readers%