%2Fnishant-tripathi-suicide-feel-like-living-corpse-mothers-emotional-note-after-mumbai-mans-suicide-7868615%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Trump's%2010%25%20Tariffs%20Are%20Barely%20Enough%20To%20Make%20Xi%20Blink%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20brinkmanship%20with%20China%20is%20escalating%20with%20the%20announcement%20of%20a%20fresh%2010%25%20tariff%2C%20along%20with%2025%25%20duties%20on%20imports%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20on%20March%204.%20Given%20the%2010%25%20levy%20imposed%20by%20the%20US%20that%20came%20into%20effect%20last%20month%2C%20Chinese%20exports%20to%20the%20U.S.%20are%20set%20to%20face%20duties%20of%20up%20to%2020%25%20at%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Trump's%20first%20terms%2C%20tariffs%20valued%20at%20nearly%20%24380%20billion%20had%20been%20imposed%20on%20Chinese%20products.%20Later%2C%20towards%20the%20end%2C%20both%20parties%20conciliated%20and%20inked%20a%20deal%20to%20redress%20the%20issue%20of%20trade%20deficit.%20Under%20phase%20I%20of%20the%20US-China%20trade%20deal%20in%202020%2C%20Beijing%20had%20pledged%20to%20increase%20imports%20from%20Washington%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20%24200%20billion%20over%20a%20span%20of%20two%20years.%20However%2C%20Trump%2C%20after%20beginning%20his%20second%20stint%20as%20President%2C%20has%20now%20indicated%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20put%20the%20Phase%20I%20deal%20back%20on%20the%20table%20to%20give%20US%20businesses%20equitable%20access%20to%20the%20Chinese%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Unreliable%20Entities'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20trade%20deficit%20looms%20large%20even%20five%20years%20later.%20In%202024%2C%20Washington's%20imports%20from%20Beijing%20stood%20at%20%24438.9%20billion%2C%20an%20increase%20of%202.8%25%20compared%20to%202023%2C%20according%20to%20statistics%20compiled%20by%20the%20US%20Trade%20Representative's%20office.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Chinese%20imports%20from%20the%20US%20were%20%24143.5%20billion%20in%202024%2C%20a%20decrease%20of%202.9%25%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%20Thus%2C%20last%20year%2C%20America's%20trade%20deficit%20in%20goods%20with%20China%20was%20%24295.4%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20America's%20actions%2C%20China%20has%20announced%2015%25%20tariffs%20on%20wheat%2C%20corn%2C%20cotton%20and%20poultry%2C%20in%20addition%20to%2010%25%20duties%20on%20soybean%2C%20dairy%20products%2C%20pork%20and%20beef.%20Not%20just%20that%2C%20it%20has%20added%2010%20American%20firms%20to%20its%20%E2%80%98unreliable%20entities%20list'%20over%20the%20sale%20of%20weapons%20to%20Taiwan%2C%20while%2015%20American%20companies%20have%20been%20put%20on%20the%20export%20control%20list.%20Biotech%20major%20Illumina%2C%20which%20already%20has%20the%20%E2%80%98unreliable%20entity'%20tag%2C%20is%20prohibited%20from%20selling%20its%20gene-sequencing%20devices%20on%20the%20mainland.%20US%20fibre-optic%20products%20are%20also%20under%20the%20lens%20over%20anti-dumping%20policies%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Beijing%20promulgated%20the%20Export%20Control%20Law%2C%20which%20prohibits%20the%20overseas%20sale%20of%20strategic%20materials%20and%20advanced%20know-how%20to%20specific%20foreign%20entities.%20The%20%E2%80%98unreliable%20entities%20list'%20includes%20foreign%20companies%20and%20individuals%20that%20are%20said%20to%20impinge%20upon%20Chinese%20interests.%20It%20came%20into%20being%20in%20response%20to%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration's%20action%20against%20Huawei%20and%20its%20addition%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98entity%20list'%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20the%20company%20had%20hurt%20American%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgriculture%20Focus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20is%20also%20targeting%20Washington's%20agricultural%20produce%2C%20which%20rose%20to%2015%25%20of%20China's%20total%20imports%20between%202012%20and%202023%2C%20from%20merely%204%25%20in%201998-2004.%20While%20China%20imported%20nearly%20%2425%20billion%20of%20farm%20produce%20from%20the%20US%20last%20year%2C%20it%20is%20diversifying%20its%20suppliers%20and%20taking%20recourse%20to%20domestic%20substitution.%20Syngenta%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20agriculture-technology%20firms%2C%20was%20acquired%20by%20China%20for%20%2443%20billion%20in%202017.%20Going%20ahead%2C%20Beijing%20is%20prioritising%20strengthening%20food%20security%20to%20combat%20trade%20disruption%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20its%20annual%20farm-policy%20roadmap%20titled%20%E2%80%98Number%201%20document'.%20The%20new%20strategy%20aims%20to%20achieve%20self-sufficiency%20through%20subsidies%20and%20incentives%20for%20foodgrain-producing%20areas%2C%20and%20through%20the%20introduction%20of%20high-yield%20seeds.%20China%20has%20also%20decided%20to%20consolidate%20its%20%E2%80%98national%20reserves'%20and%20expedite%20the%20construction%20of%20storage%20facilities%20for%20cotton%2C%20sugar%2C%20meat%2C%20grain%2C%20and%20fertilizers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Xi%20Is%20Wooing%20The%20Private%20Sector%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20developments%20related%20to%20escalating%20tariffs%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Chinese%20elite%20congregate%20for%20a%20sitting%20of%20its%20legislative%20and%20policy-advisory%20wings%E2%80%94the%20National%20People's%20Congress%20and%20the%20Chinese%20People's%20Political%20Consultative%20Conference%E2%80%94popularly%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98two%20sessions'.%20This%20key%20event%20on%20the%20Party's%20political%20calendar%20charts%20the%20policy%20course.%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20this%20conclave%2C%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20has%20met%20with%20China%20Inc%20and%20is%20closing%20ranks%20with%20the%20country's%20entrepreneurial%20class%2C%20rehabilitating%20the%20likes%20of%20Jack%20Ma%2C%20Alibaba's%20founder%2C%20who%20had%20been%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party's%20crackdown.%20Xi%20encouraged%20them%20to%20give%20free%20rein%20to%20their%20%E2%80%9Canimal%20spirits%E2%80%9D%20with%20respect%20to%20resuscitating%20the%20economy.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20takeaways%20from%20the%20%E2%80%982%20sessions'%20was%20Xi%20telling%20cadres%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20do%20more%20to%20support%20China%20Inc.%20Thus%2C%20the%20private%20sector%20is%20back%20in%20China's%20economic%20calculus%20and%20will%20be%20expected%20to%20pool%20resources%20into%20technological%20self-sufficiency%20and%20innovation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20China's%20%E2%80%98No.%202'%2C%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%2C%20has%20already%20identified%20focus%20areas%20like%20quantum%20technology%2C%20AI%2C%20bio-manufacturing%2C%20and%206G%20technology%20in%20his%20Government%20Work%20Report.%20As%20a%20confidence-building%20measure%2C%20the%20Party-state%20has%20issued%20a%20directive%20on%20bolstering%20monetary%20support%20for%20self-reliance%20and%20innovation.%20Since%20there%20is%20a%20long%20gestation%20period%20in%20the%20development%20of%20technology%2C%20the%20new%20approach%20seeks%20to%20merge%20equity%20investment%20and%20insurance%20to%20provide%20support%20for%20technology%20companies%20at%20every%20phase%20of%20growth.%20Another%20instrument%20being%20considered%20to%20assuage%20the%20private%20sector%20is%20legislation%20that%20aims%20to%20provide%20better%20protection%20and%20a%20level-playing%20field%20to%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReally%20'Ready%20For%20War'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20sum%20up%2C%20Beijing's%20official%20response%20to%20the%20fresh%20round%20of%20Washington's%20tariffs%20has%20been%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20for%20a%20trade%20war%20or%20%E2%80%9Cany%20other%20type%20of%20war%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20it%20will%20fight%20till%20the%20very%20end.%20Nonetheless%2C%20it%20has%20also%20dangled%20a%20carrot%2C%20urging%20the%20Trump%20adm