57-mohammad-hafeez-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Hafeez%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20pace%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shoaib%20Akhtar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F381-shoaib-akhtar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShoaib%20Akhtar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20a%20discussion%20on%20PTV%20Sports%2C%20Hafeez%20questioned%20the%20legacy%20of%20players%20who%20represented%20Pakistan%20in%20the%2090s%20and%20early%202000s%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20failed%20to%20inspire%20the%20next%20generation%20by%20failing%20to%20win%20a%20number%20of%20ICC%20events%20during%20their%20time.%20Former%20Pakistan%20pacer%20Akhtar%2C%20who%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20side%20during%20the%2090s%20and%20early%202000s%2C%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20same%20discussion%2C%20but%20he%20seemed%20agitated%20while%20Hafeez%20was%20having%20a%20go%20at%20the%20former%20players.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20those%20who%20played%20in%20the%201990s%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20legacy%2C%20they%20left%20nothing%20for%20Pakistan.%20They%20didn't%20win%20an%20ICC%20event%20-%20they%20lost%20the%20(World%20Cups%20of)%201996%2C%201999%20and%202003.%20We%20reached%20one%20final%20(in%20the%201999%20World%20Cup)%20and%20lost%20that%20badly.%20As%20stars%2C%20as%20players%2C%20they%20were%20the%20mega%20superstars.%20But%20then%20they%20couldn't%20inspire%20us%20by%20winning%20an%20ICC%20event.%20Then%20came%20a%20difficult%20period%20that%20we%20had%20to%20go%20through%20and%20then%20in%202007%20we%20lost%20the%20final%20(of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup).%2C%26quot%3B%20Hafeez%20said%20on%20PTV%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20Hafeez%20lauded%20Pakistan's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20(2009)%20and%20Champions%20Trophy%20(2017)%20winning%20sides.%20He%20also%20explained%20why%20players%20like%20Babar%20Azam%20get%20idolised%20by%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20In%202009%20we%20won%20under%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Younis%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F454-younus-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYounis%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E's%20captaincy%20and%20so%20there%20was%20an%20inspiration%20for%20the%20next%20generation.%20Then%20unfortunately%20a%20bad%20incident%20happened%20with%20Pakistan%20cricket%20and%20we%20have%20still%20not%20been%20able%20to%20recover%20from%20that.%20Then%20we%20won%20the%202017%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20that%20was%20a%20huge%20source%20of%20inspiration.%20People%20idolise%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20and%20that%20is%20because%20even%20if%20he%20didn't%20play%20a%20big%20hand%20in%20that%20event%2C%20he%20was%20there.%20So%20that%20thing%20about%20winning%20ICC%20events%2C%20this%20the%20superstars%20of%20the%201990s%20couldn't%20do%2C%20with%20all%20due%20respect%20to%20their%20talents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Pakistan%20cricketers%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shoaib%20Malik%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F382-shoaib-malik-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShoaib%20Malik%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sana%20Mir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F62243-sana-mir-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESana%20Mir%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ex-women's%20team%20captain)%20tried%20to%20intervene%2C%20sparking%20a%20laughing%20riot%20inside%20the%20studio.%20Even%20Akhtar%20was%20seen%20smiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Akhtar%20questioned%20Hafeez%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThese%2073%20one-dayers%20that%20Pakistan%20won%20against%20India%2C%20it%20is%20us%20who%20won%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESomeone%20had%20to%20do%20it%2C%20some%20fixers%20and