y%20the%20victim's%20mother%20Neelam%20Chaturvedi%2C%20a%20women's%20rights%20activist.%20No%20one%20has%20been%20arrested%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20suicide%20note%2C%20which%20was%20secured%20with%20a%20password%20on%20his%20company's%20website%2C%20he%20expressed%20his%20love%20for%20his%20wife%20and%20held%20her%20and%20her%20aunt%20responsible%20for%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20time%20you%20read%20this%2C%20I'll%20be%20gone.%20In%20my%20last%20moments%2C%20I%20could've%20hated%20you%20for%20everything%20that%20happened.%20But%20I%20don't.%20For%20this%20moment%2C%20I%20choose%20love.%20I%20loved%20you%20then.%20I%20love%20you%20now.%20And%20as%20I%20had%20promised%2C%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20fade%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20his%20suicide%20note.%20%26quot%3BMy%20mother%20knows%20among%20all%20the%20other%20struggles%20I%20faced%2C%20you%20and%20Prarthana%20Mausi%20are%20also%20responsible%20for%20my%20death.%20So%20I%20beg%20you%20don't%20approach%20her%20now.%20She's%20broken%20enough.%20Let%20her%20grieve%20in%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Chaturvedi%20wrote%20a%20long%20post%20on%20Facebook%20grieving%20her%20son's%20death.%20%26quot%3BToday%20I%20feel%20like%20a%20living%20corpse%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20devoted%20her%20life%20to%20women's%20rights%20and%20gender%20equality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20life%20is%20over%20now.%20My%20son%2C%20Nishant%20left%20me.%20I%20have%20now%20become%20a%20living%20corpse.%20He%20had%20to%20perform%20my%20last%20rites%20but%20today%20on%202nd%20March%2C%20I%20have%20cremated%20my%20son%20at%20%26quot%3BECO-MOKSHA%26quot%3B%20Mumbai.%20My%20daughter%20Prachi%20performed%20the%20last%20rites%20of%20her%20elder%20brother.%20Give%20me%20and%20my%20daughter%20Prachi%20courage%20so%20that%20I%20can%20bear%20such%20a%20big%20thunderbolt%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20her%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes